* Copa LG Electonics 1999 (Cd. de Guatemala)

BlockSource: http://www.rsssf.com/tablesl/lgclub99.html

Competition: Copa LG Electronics
Season: 1999

* 23-25 July 1999 in Cd. de Guatemala(Estadio "Mateo Flores")

*Participants:
*Antigua G.F.C. (Guatemala)
*Municipal (Guatemala)
*FAS (El Salvador)
*Saprissa (Costa Rica)

Round: Semifinals

